Purpose: L0 specR cloning to CDS2 overhangs

L0 specR mutant cloning. In brief, for each stop codon, PCRs B and A were set up using the corresponding stop codon primers and the corresponding general Gibson primers. They were then purified and assembled through Gibson reaction.
